{"$content":[{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_00_000","SpeakerName":"","SpeakerAssetName":"","IconName":"","IconLocate":1,"Text":"Three years later...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_00_001","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Morris...","sfxName":"h0025_story_021","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_00_002","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"The headmaster is asking what we are doing moving so many things to this old storage room again.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_00_003","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You still haven't solved that formula?","sfxName":"h0025_story_020","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_00_004","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Yeah. If we want it to not be easily manipulated by other things, the Guardian must have a basic level of self-consciousness...","sfxName":"h0043_story_020_ver2","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_00_005","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Allowing a lifeless item to have a conscious while at the same time making it follow commands and operate stably...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_00_006","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Is this truly impossible...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_000","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Hmph, looks like we'll just have to gamble on it!","sfxName":"h0043_story_004","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_001","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Charle, go and get some rubbings of the stone tablets on the prairie!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_002","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You want to decrypt the mysterious runes carved on the stone tablets?","sfxName":"h0025_story_005","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_003","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"But even the Academy has not even decrypted a small fraction of those carvings!","sfxName":"h0025_story_010","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_004","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Being stuck here with no solution is not an option. A quick detour might just give us the spark we need.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_005","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Alright then. I just finished teaching my class. I'll get going right away. You get some rest first.","sfxName":"h0025_story_024","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_006","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Understood. If I get hungry, I'll fix dinner myself.","sfxName":"h0043_story_022","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_007","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I might accidentally make too much...so when you come back, let's eat together.","sfxName":"h0043_story_005","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_008","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Thanks.","sfxName":"h0025_story_025","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_009","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Next time, let me cook for a change.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_01_010","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I've studied quite a bit of cooking myself too~","sfxName":"h0025_story_013","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_02_013","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"M-Must not give him the chance to cook no matter what...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_02_014","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Where the heck did he get the confidence when it comes to cooking? Baffles me to no end.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_03_000","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Hmm, judging by the marks on the map, I should be done rubbing all the stone tablets around this area.","sfxName":"h0025_story_012","sfxVolume":0.3},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_000","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":""Stone tablets are messages passed down by the ancient people."

"They contain massive amounts of currently unknown ancient knowledge."","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_001","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"The research speculations that have been there since the founding days of Rune Academy, will they really help us complete the Runic Guardian?","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_002","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"By the way...","sfxName":"h0025_story_020","sfxVolume":0.4},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_003","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_sorrow","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I feel so tired after just one little run.","sfxName":"h0025_story_003","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_004","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I've spent the last several years cooped up in the school doing experiments. Could it be that I'm just now feeling the after-effects?","sfxName":"h0025_story_010","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_005","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_sorrow","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Can we really finish the Runic Guardian without a hitch...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_006","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"The sound of combat?","sfxName":"h0025_story_005","sfxVolume":0.7},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_007","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Clovis!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_008","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Ceres?","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_009","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Hmph, so it's you...","sfxName":"h0005_story_002","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_010","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Clovis, deal with the monsters first!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_04_011","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Yes.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_05_000","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Didn't expect to see you at a place like this. When did you develop an interest in history as well?","sfxName":"h0005_story_013","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_05_001","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I wasn't interested until I heard Morris' explanation. I've also started to understand some of the basics.","sfxName":"h0025_story_021","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_05_002","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Professor Dietrich? He's with you? What exactly is he so busy about these days?","sfxName":"h0005_story_019","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_05_003","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Oh, right. You became a newly-appointed teacher two months ago. I don't think you two have seen each other since then...","sfxName":"h0025_story_020","sfxVolume":0.4},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_06_000","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"We are trying to figure out a method from these ancient tablets that can allow the Runic Guardian to operate.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_06_001","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"However, Morris still hasn't solved the key formulas...","sfxName":"h0025_story_003","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_06_002","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Hmph, what makes you the one?","sfxName":"h0005_story_002","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_06_003","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"What?","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_07_000","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You don't have what it takes to help him. Take me to professor Dietrich.","sfxName":"h0005_story_018","sfxVolume":0.4},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_07_001","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"...Alrighty.","sfxName":"h0025_story_003","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_07_002","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Charle, I've reached an agreement with the headmaster. I'll move my private lab to this location.","sfxName":"h0043_story_005","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_07_003","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Afterward, when we apply for experiment equipment, we can...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_08_000","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Clovis? Why the hell are you here!","sfxName":"h0043_story_023","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_08_001","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Apologies. I figured that Clovis might be able to help us out.","sfxName":"h0025_story_026","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_08_002","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Why did you make this decision on your own? I never asked for help! Or did you think that I don't have what it takes to solve this problem!","sfxName":"h0043_story_004","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_09_000","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"The formulas I previously wrote have been erased!? Who gave you two the permission to do such a thing!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_09_001","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Professor Dietrich, please take a closer look.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_10_000","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"A solution like this exists?","sfxName":"h0043_story_012","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_10_001","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_surprise","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Although it takes a small detour, it provides space for a change here, which then allows the purpose to be fulfilled. Why didn't I think of this?","sfxName":"h0043_story_021","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_11_000","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You solved all of this yourself?","sfxName":"h0043_story_005","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_11_001","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Yes. Ceres didn't help in any shape or form.","sfxName":"h0005_story_018","sfxVolume":0.4},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_11_002","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Gotta hand it to you, Clovis...you really are amazing...","sfxName":"h0043_story_020_ver1","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_000","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"What are you so depressed about, Mr. Genius?
With this, the experiment can keep going, right?","sfxName":"h0025_story_013","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_001","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Yes. Looks like we can perform the experiment again in just a few days.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_002","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Professor Dietrich, can I accompany you?","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_003","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Clovis, you're the one who solved this formula. Of course you...","sfxName":"h0025_story_021","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_004","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Nope. No~~pe~","sfxName":"h0043_story_001","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_005","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"This is not something a person of your level should come in contact with. Regarding this case, I will find some other time to thank you.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_006","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"We're about to conduct the next phase. You should leave right now!","sfxName":"h0043_story_011","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_007","SpeakerName":"Aosta","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0005","IconName":"h0005s4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"But...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_008","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Charle, let's perform the final adjustments right away!","sfxName":"h0043_story_006","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_009","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Morris, didn't expect that it would be your student who saved us.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_010","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You talk too much. You should hurry and set up the formations!","sfxName":"h0043_story_004","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_011","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Yes, professor Dietrich~","sfxName":"h0025_story_011","sfxVolume":0.5},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_012","SpeakerName":"Morris","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0043","IconName":"h0043s5_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You little...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0025_004_dialog_english##_12_013","SpeakerName":"Charle","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0025","IconName":"h0025s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Hahaha~","sfxName":"h0025_story_013","sfxVolume":0.5}]}
